<p>All sounds amazing, right? In fact, it seems almost too good to be true.</p>
<p>But here’s the thing: we’re offering these at ‘good tasting treat’ prices rather than ‘fix your dog’s joints’ prices. And sure, they’re a bit close to their best-by date, but they’re still worth a shot, right?</p>
<p>So give them a try. And, by that, we mean: give them to your dog. Don’t take them for your own joints.</p>